data.description: WOW, SELLER GIVING 2% TOWARDS CLOSING COST, PREPAIDS OR 2/1 LOAN RATE BUYDOWN! Built in 2020, Chelsea Model w/5 bedrooms, 4 bathrooms w/loft, flex room & 3 car garage on one of the largest lots in sought after Arden Community! Kitchen has dark wood cabinets, Quartz counter tops, white glass tile backsplash, island w/under mount drop sink, stainless steel gas range, double oven, microwave, dishwasher & refrigerator. Large Pantry! Wood plank title throughout the first floor! One bedroom down stairs & bathroom. Second floor: Huge Master Bedroom w/walk in closet. Master bath w/dual sinks, glass enclosed shower & water closet. Nice size loft! 3 sizable bedrooms, one w/own bath & 1 w/Jack & Jill bath. Laundry room! Impact window & doors throughout! Gated community w/tons of amenities! A+ schools
